Package: GLLAMMR
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Linear Latent and Mixed Models
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-02-06
Authors@R: c(
    person("Josh", "", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "Sonnet 4.5", role = "ctb", comment = "Implementation assistant"))
Description: Comprehensive implementation of Generalized Linear Latent and Mixed
    Models (GLLAMM) following the Stata GLLAMM framework by Rabe-Hesketh, Skrondal,
    and Pickles. Supports multilevel generalized linear models (GLMMs), factor models,
    item response theory (IRT) models, latent class models, and structural equation
    models with mixed response types. Uses Template Model Builder (TMB) for efficient
    computation via automatic differentiation.
